page.title: 09High Wycombe Superstore
page.content: {Asda}is the main attraction in our square.Lots of people come from far away to{shop}at this supermarket.Our custom is to collect a trolley and push it through the entrance then go around the shop collecting all the things needed.There would be things like food,sweets,electrical appliances like toasters and kettles.Drinks,wines and clothes.You can buy some{health} foods like yoghurt and cheese.All food is wrapped to keep it clean.When you have collected all you need you go and pay for them.The things go through an{ {electric-eye.}To pay for the things you can use{cheque,cash}or{bankcards.} When you finish you can go to the restaurant which is part of our lifestyle.
